  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Galvus as add-on Therapy to Metformin Plus Glimepiride</brief_title>
  <acronym>Vildagliptin</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind Placebo Controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of 24 Weeks Treatment With Vildagliptin 50 mg Bid as add-on Therapy to Metformin Plus Glimepiride in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
