  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy and safety of vildagliptin 50 mg bid as add-on therapy
      to metformin plus glimepiride in patients with Type 2 Diabetes (T2D).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
